\f3\b0 \cf0  \cf5 theTable\cf0  \cf4 grid style\cf0  
\f4\i \cf9 grid between columns
\f3\i0 \cf0  \cf4 highlighted rows\cf0  \{1, 2\} 
\f2\b with
\f3\b0  \cf4 alternate backgrounds\cf0 \

